      "title": "Common Git Commands",
      "file": "package.json",
      "line": 1,
      "description": "## Git Command Reference\n\n### Everyday commands:\n\n```bash\n# See what changed\ngit status\n\n# See line-by-line changes\ngit diff\n\n# Add files to commit\ngit add <file>\ngit add .\n\n# Commit changes\ngit commit -m \"message\"\n\n# Push to GitHub\ngit push\n\n# Get latest from GitHub\ngit pull\n```\n\n### Branch commands:\n```bash\n# See all branches\ngit branch\n\n# Create and switch to branch\ngit checkout -b branch-name\n\n# Switch to existing branch\ngit checkout branch-name\n\n# Delete a branch\ngit branch -d branch-name\n```\n\n### Viewing history:\n```bash\n# See commit history\ngit log --oneline\n\n# See who changed each line\ngit blame file.tsx\n```"
